values: Heh, yeah. I'm back up with my livejournal. Not like anyone really minds or anything, I have like 2 friends on here. xD I'm spending more time here on LJ cause I've become aware of the communities here and hope to join a few. ^-^ I BADLY need an icon. Like now plz. I need to get off my tail and make one. oo;; Lucky has gotten better at drawing people now. They're not great, but I'm happy with them. XD Maybe I can steal talent from Nikki or something. (heh heh, just kiddin') I have become very fond of the band Gorillaz and the anime One Piece. OP has become my new anime obsession.. I hope to have fanart up on my deviantART account soon, and I'd love to tackle a fanfiction if I wasn't so scared of typing the characters OOC. Yush... and mind you, I could rant for hours about the gawd-awful English dub of OP. I'm so glad I found fansubs of the Japanese version. ^^ <3 *is hooked* I still love Detective Conan, too! I just think my obsession on that one has been put on a hiatus or something. XB So, yush. Lucky out!

I've been feeling very under the weather lately, and lots of people have been wishing me well on deviantART. ^-^ Even some people who I forgot were watching me wished me get well. It makes me feel so much better, it really does. Then somebody suggested that I get a hug counter, and I thought that wasn't a bad idea. The only problem was, I don't have a subscription to dA and it won't let me post IMGs in journal entries. So I just figured that I could post everthing except the IMG counter on dA, post the counter on here, and update the number of hugs I recieve on dA in the journal entry. So, yeah. Here's the hug counter:

*HUGS* TOTAL! give Aoi-Kitsune more *HUGS*
Get hugs of your own
^^;;; heh heh!! ~Lucky
OMG! Check out my Gaia avatar: I'm completely blue!! Everything except my skin color is blue. :D *is obsessed*

A ton of my friends from school convinced me to try out gaiaonline.com, and I tried it because I've heard Dyani speak of it before. And I found that it looks so super incredibly fun!! Even though all I have is this black rag-like thing and shockingly blue hair. ^^;; I really want at least a pair of pants, but I find that 305 gaian gold is not worth much. I fell in love with the fox ears and fox tail, which I really want, but getting gold is hard. Nya. I want pants. NOW.

I now have a role-playing forum; anyone's allowed to join. I rped with a friend from an oekaki and I am suddenly really excited about it for some weird reason. She drew me a picture of my character in the rp, and I love it to death!! I never used to really like it, but Role Play is really fun!! ^^

One thing a lot of people don't know about me is that I'm a DJ. ^^ I recently DJed at my school's 6th grade social, and the teachers told me I was the best DJ they ever had. That's really sayin' something, since they've been there over 30-40 years. ^^ So yesh, I am really proud of myself.

I'm back from Cali!! And I spent five whole days in Disneyland. ^^; And one whole day in Universal. I could go on and on and on and on and on for how my trip went. I might go back a few days on the journal and make entries on the dates of everything that I can remember. The highlights of the trip?

Heh, I'm new to LJ. *knows nothing about it* Would someone be so kind as to help me? I know a few people on DeviantART who have an account. Maybe I can find a few here. ^^;;;

~Lucky
